reviewText: A very detailed instruction. Although it seems pricy, the video has over 3 hours of detailed instruction and tips. I am now using it to try my own project. Great content and easy to follow!

Cynthia Garza does a superb job demonstrating how to make theatrical fake teeth. In addition to her outstanding presentation, sound, lighting, and videography are excellent. I recommend this presentation for anybody desiring to make Hollywood quality fake teeth. I give this presentation a five star rating.
